# py-mini-emulator

A simple, open-source, extendable emulator scaffold for learning and experimentation.

## Features
- CPU simulation (basic instruction execution)
- Memory management
- Display output
- Easy to extend

## Getting Started
1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/vegasdude/py-mini-emulator.git

## Reference

